caption:
SO CRISPY 🔥⁣
⁣
Comment “shrimp balls” and I will send you a recipe 😘⁣
⁣
I can’t believe I’ve NEVER tried this dim sum classic till now, and I have to say, it’s absolutely INCREDIBLE!⁣
⁣
Typically, the shrimp filling is coated with spring roll wrappers, but I decided to coat them with @omsom Soy Garlic Saucy Noodles, and it turned out EVEN BETTER than I thought 😮‍💨⁣
⁣
The savory noodles created an extremely crispy texture outside, almost like crispy noodle chip, while the shrimp filling stayed SO juicy and flavorful ✨⁣
⁣
Y’ALL HAVE TO TRY THIS 👏🏽⁣
⁣
